surveyor 0.1-15 (13/11/2011)
---------------

Improvements:
* Fixes to plots, e.g. word-wrap of main title, lattice column plot layout.


surveyor 0.1-14 (7/11/2011)
---------------

New features:
* Support for output to PowerPoint, using package braidppt (which depends on R2PPT)

surveyor 0.1-13 (1/11/2011)
---------------

New features:
* Added support to specify graphic format (i.e. pdf / wmf) for graphics

surveyor 0.1-11
---------------

New features:
* surveyorPlot uses the package::braid mechanism to only generate plots when the code or data has changed.
* codeQuickArray is now the default code function.  It is quicker than codeArray and also handles codeSingle
* Now exports paste_percent.


surveyor 0.1-08
---------------

New features:
* Converted all functions and arguments to use camelCase.
* Integrated surveydata package.  surveyor data type must be of class surveydata.

surveyor 0.1-0
--------------

First alpha.